content:
To limit the height of images within the `.card` class, you can add the `max-height` property directly to the `img` selector:
```css
.card img {
  border-radius: 2em;
  max-width: 90%;
  max-height: 200px; /* set your desired max-height here */
  padding: 0.5em;
}
```
Adjust the value of `max-height` to your desired height. The `max-height` property limits the height of the image, while the `max-width` property limits the width of the image.
